		<h3>Reflection</h3> 
		<h4>Account for all requirements into the design</h4> 
		<p>
		Our team spent a lot of time downsizing the robot due to its heavy weight 
		as we overlooked a requirement to maintain a maximum weight of 6kg for the robot. 
		After designing the robot, we figured it would be best to build the entire robot with wood as that was Tommy’s expertise.
		We later regretted our decision when we found out that the robot’s weight was more than 6kg. 
		We spent 20 hours reducing the robot’s weight to 6kg.
		</p>
		
